reviewText: Do not be hoodwinked---I love movies and this is what I thought it was, it is hard to know what you are buying off of this site but thru this reviews you can do your due diligence. This is a guess a documentary though I would not even say that. I do not know what this is. I wish I could get my money back. It is worthless
at first I thought this was a movie, but when I began to watch it as saw it was a documentary I found it very interesting.
Ok for the price hard to follow
I liked this documentary.  It sparked a lot of conversation between me and friends.  I will recommend it to others.
